misc: armchina-npu: restore local Sky1 ACPI DMA and lifetime fixes for 6.18.35

Keep the imported CIX userspace ABI while restoring the local ACPI, DMA API,
probe-deferral, IRQ and dma-buf lifetime fixes needed by the Orion O6/O6N
ACPI kernel builds.

